name: UFO: Mission unknown
description:
Simple game made in 3 hours for TriJam 205. Theme "Secret Mission".

You were sent to the Earth to collect some species, but you totally forgot the exact species and collection order. Now details of your mission are secret to yourself.

WASD - control UFO

Space - enable tractor beam.

Every incorrect specie you collect resets all your level progress.

There are three levels, and the third one is really insane
